    "stat_block": {
        "type": "stat_block",
        "subtype": "equipment",
        "text": "Druids and Calistria's faithful alike value this vindictive armor for its ability to turn away pests and exact revenge on foes in a manner that can easily turn coordinated enemies into a chaotic mass. *Wasp guard* is *+1 studded leather* studded with the carapaces of wasps, subtly diverting swarms away and granting a +1 status bonus to Reflex saving throws against Swarming Bites, Swarming Stings, and similar abilities from swarms.",
        "level": 8,
